            "failure_message": "Mild irritation must stay small: keeps rage/contempt/disgust low, caps smoldering_anger tightly (to avoid cold sustained hostility), and limits arousal/control so heavier anger states route elsewhere. Still requires a crossing/spike so it doesn't spam as a baseline."
