    "actor_description": "Something keeps scraping at me-small, persistent, impossible to ignore. I feel my patience thinning, a tightness gathering at my jaw and behind my eyes. I'm not ready to blow up. I'm justâ€¦ done with this. My thoughts get shorter, sharper; I want whatever's causing it to stop, move, or get fixed. I keep catching myself on the edge of a snap, then swallowing it back.",
